title: "Garf's Analytics"
output: html_notebook
---
Load Packages
```{r, include=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
```

Read in the data
```{r, include=FALSE}
garfs <- read_csv("Garfs CSV")
```
Parse Dates
```{r, include=FALSE}
garfs$Date <- mdy(garfs$Date)
```

Inspect
```{r}
str(garfs)
```

```{r}
summary(garfs)
```

```{r}
head(garfs)
```

Let's try plotting something

```{r}
ggplot(data = garfs, aes(x = Date, y = Made)) + 
    geom_line()
```

    

Test dates
```{r}
month(garfs)
```
